high_descs: Go to the island across from the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the island.
Go to the end of the counter next to the shelf.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Go to the trash can on the right of the fridge.
Put the butter knife in the trash.
Go to the end of the counter next to the shelf.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge.
Move over to the right of the fridge to the trash can.
Put the cold bread in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in the trash.

high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to face the middle of it.
Pick up the dinner knife in the middle of the kitchen island.
Walk around the kitchen island, hanging a left to reach the counter on the right of the brown shelf.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter with the dinner knife.
Turn right to walk around the island, hanging a right, then stopping at the trash can to the right of the fridge.
Put the dinner knife in the trash can.
Turn left, walking back to the counter by hanging a left around the island.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn right, then turn right again at the island to reach the fridge.
Chill the bread slice in the fridge, removing it afterwards.
Turn to face the trash can next to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of bread, throwing a slice of bread and the knife in the trash can.

high_descs: Go to the sink and turn right, then turn towards the loaf of bread on the kitchen island.
Pick up the butter knife to the left of the pan, on the island.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the island, then turn left and go to the counter on your right, just past the stove.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the sink, then turn right again and go to the garbage bin on the floor to just after the refrigerator, on your left.
Place the knife in the garbage bin.
Turn to your left and go to the end of the island, then turn left and go to the end of the counter top on your right.
Pick up one of the slices of bread.
Turn to your right and go to the sink, then turn to your right again and go to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the slice of bread on the top shelf of the refrigerator, to the left of the egg, wait a moment for the bread to chill, then remove the bread from the refrigerator.
Go to the garbage bin on the floor to the right of the refrigerator.
Place the slice of bread in the garbage bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a cold slice of bread in the garbage.
